==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Totemism
<hw>To"tem*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
system of distinguishing families, clans, etc., in a tribe by the
totem.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Superstitious regard for a totem; the worship of any
real or imaginary object; nature worship.</def>
<rj><au>Tylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Totemist</ent>⟦br⟧
